             - <rs id="t18301028-14-verdict94" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18301028-14-verdict94" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs> - DEATH. Aged 24.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18301028-14-punish95" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18301028-14-punish95" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18301028-14-punish95" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="respitedForPregnancy"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301028-14-defend232 t18301028-14-punish95"></join>
               The prisoner on being called up for judgment, pleaded that she was with quick child, which plea, a Jury of matrons having affirmed, her judgment stands respited
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>WILLIAM ODDY - <rs id="t18301028-14-verdict96" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18301028-14-verdict96" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
